        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Matthew saith that Christ spake this to the Pharisees, who were very far from acknowledging Christ God man, or indeed expecting a Messiah that should be so. Had they owned Christ, and the hypostatical union of the two natures in him, the answer had been easy. ",
        "children": []
